    "We also obtained layered understanding and reflections through reflective practices like memo writing (Fig. 2), which are presented in Section 6.",
    "We performed open coding to generate codes from the qualitative data of the initial set of 13 articles.",
    "Open coding was done for each line of the 'Findings' sections of the included articles to ensure we did not miss any information and insights related to our research question (RQ).",
